        <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">aletto Potsdamer Platz</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">3-minute walk from Gleisdreieck U-Bahn station, 6-min walk to the venue. From 160€ a night.</p>
	</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
